gmd:abstract.gco:CharacterString: The European environment information and observation network (Eionet) spatial data sets include information about European river basin districts, river basin district sub-units, surface water bodies, groundwater bodies and monitoring sites. The dataset includes Switzerland, Turkey and the West Balkan countries, as well as historical data for EU Member States, Norway and Iceland.
